Package src.symbol

Class Klass

java.lang.Object
src.semantics.Binding
src.symbol.Klass
public class Klass extends Binding
Represents a class declaration in the program's symbol handling phase. Klass class extends the Binding class and is used to store information about a class, including its methods and global variables.
